Compressing objects: 100% (11/11), done.
Writing objects: 100% (11/11), 25.81 KiB | 0 bytes/s, done.
Total 11 (delta 2), reused 0 (delta 0)
To https://github.com/ruhigit/Git_Basics.git
   4ed5a58..1f96799  master -> master

